Package com.tractrac.model.lib.api.spatial

Interface IGeoCoordinate

All Known Subinterfaces:
IPosition, IPositionSnapped
public interface IGeoCoordinate

A geographical coordinate.

The position is in the WGS84 coordinate frame.

A geographical coordinate may and may not have a height. If height is not valid, a value of Double.NaN must be returned

Author:
Jesper Grooss
